    <h3>Stealth power.</h3>
    <p>StarBook Mk V looks unassuming in matte black anodized aluminum, but it’s engineered to pack a punch. 11th-gen Intel Core processors deliver performance on demand while sipping power. Low-latency memory keeps everything snappy. And the over-provisioned solid state StarDrive offers incredible speeds for opening your apps and files.</p>
