  <section id="display">
    <img alt="StarBook Mk V" loading="lazy" src="<%= Routes.static_path(Endpoint, "/images/devices/starbook/hinge.png") %>" />
    <div>
      <h3>Matte or glossy—why not both?</h3>
      <p>The 14-inch ARC display features a protective hard coating that lets color shine through like glass while diffusing ambient light like a matte display. Combined with IPS technology and 400 nits of brightness, the display is visible in nearly any light and angle. Which is convenient, because the 180° hinge lets you get some pretty wild angles.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="trackpad">
    <div>
      <h3>Slip and swipe.</h3>
      <p>Glide across the 5.5-inch-diagonal glass trackpad for precise and smooth multi-touch gestures. Scroll through documents or web pages, fly through your workspaces, and swipe to go back throughout elementary OS—all with 1:1 gestures that perfectly track your fingers.</p>
    </div>
    <img alt="StarBook Mk V" loading="lazy" src="<%= Routes.static_path(Endpoint, "/images/devices/starbook/trackpad.png") %>" />
