  <div>
    <h3>A keyboard that’s pure function.</h3>
    <p>Choose a US or UK layout featuring comfortable backlit keys with snappy scissor mechanisms. Tap a single key to switch between F1 through F12 or function keys that control volume, media, brightness, and more. Plus, an extra column of handy keys including Home, End, and Page Up/Down.</p>
  </div>
  </section>

  <section id="privacy">
    <img alt="StarBook Mk V" loading="lazy" src="<%= Routes.static_path(Endpoint, "/images/devices/starbook/privacy.png") %>" />
    <h3>Ready for remote, with privacy built-in.</h3>
    <p>The HD webcam is flanked by stereo microphones for clear video and voice calls. The bright white indicator shines any time the camera is on, while elementary OS lets you know any time the mics are being accessed.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="connectivity">
    <img alt="StarBook Mk V" loading="lazy" src="<%= Routes.static_path(Endpoint, "/images/devices/starbook/side.png") %>" />
  <h3>Versatile connectivity.</h3>
  <p>Wi-Fi 6 and Bluetooth 5.1 for all things wireless. USB-C with Thunderbolt 4, power delivery, and display support for charging, accessories, output all in one. Full-size USB 3 on each side. HDMI for easy output virtually everywhere. Combination headphone/microphone jack. And a microSD card slot for expansion, mobile device file transfers, or flashing maker projects—you name it.</p>
  </section>

